{"tid":637699,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★中電要求燒焊技工需持美國機械工程學會牌照！","createTime":"2018-04-22T05:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T04:50:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1d3d81035ea7860ef358fd0d0b1b28296a2b6ac4","tid":637699,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T05:14:25.000Z","msg":"金屬銲接從業員協會及中華電力公司華員職工會指出，政府未有提供相關技能培訓及訂立高壓焊接發牌制度，質疑是有意打壓本地工人，藉此引入外勞。<br />\n<br />\n中華電力華員職工會主席施生弟表示，中電目前只有3個燒焊技工，他們均沒有美國機械工程學會階段9的牌照，而中電新發電廠新建發電機組工程，預計需要50至70名需要擁有相關新技術牌照的工人，並已透過承建商進行招聘。<br />\n<br />\n施生弟指，要取得有關牌照，需要額外3個月的培訓並通過考試，招聘條件太高，現有的燒焊工未必可以符合資格投考，而且招聘需時，以日薪計的燒焊工，可能擔心因參加招聘失去工作日數而影響收入，令他們申請時卻步，他質疑中電是藉此輸入外勞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1392509-20180422.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1392509-20180422.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=1TjRAgKfIFbsuTug5DMmHZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=e13afe61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1392509-20180422.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cd134a9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1392509-20180422.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e14cefd00f24f7d7c3d2bcbfc947ba4158e5c420","tid":637699,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T05:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a413b2094ea35920e4f95427fce46d7264047042","tid":637699,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T05:16:03.000Z","msg":"紥鐵要唔要BC?"},{"pid":"1da187b2940b6cb0575434a4421e6d07d44ef5c9","tid":637699,"uid":25866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04